## About Carolin

Carolin Desirée Toepfer is a **tech entrepreneur, CISO, and speaker** specializing in **cybersecurity, responsible AI, and digital transformation**. She combines **business expertise with a human-centric approach** to make organizations secure, efficient, and successful.  

With over a decade of experience in **digital product design, IT security, AI implementation, and business growth**, Carolin helps regulated enterprises turn complex processes into actionable, secure workflows.

---

## Workshops & Courses

**Secure Digital Process Design & Responsible AI (2 Days)**  
- Map, optimize, and secure workflows while safely leveraging AI  
- Develop internal “process mining ambassadors”  
- Focus on efficiency, compliance, and measurable business results  

**From Zero to Cybersecurity Certification**  
- Hands-on training from foundational concepts to certified practitioner  
- Skills in risk assessment, secure system design, and threat mitigation  
- Teams leave ready to implement cybersecurity best practices  

